  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="byline" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
      <svg class="byline__mark" viewBox="0 0 64 64" role="img" aria-label="TechBrot"><rect width="64" height="64" rx="14" fill="#0E4A50"></rect><g transform="translate(12.16 12.16) scale(0.62)" fill="#FCFBF8"><path d="M8 10 H38 V54 H26 V22 H8 Z"></path><rect x="42" y="10" width="14" height="12"></rect></g></svg>
      <div><p class="byline__name">By the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team</p><p class="byline__review">TechBrot Inc. &middot; Independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>This page reflects how TechBrot handles New York medical-practice engagements. It is maintained by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, a Delaware-incorporated independent ProAdvisor firm, and reviewed for technical accuracy on payer reconciliation, aged A/R, provider payroll, and the New York professional-entity rules (<a href="https://dos.ny.gov/professional-corporation-pllc" rel="noopener nofollow">PC / PLLC professional entities</a> under the state&rsquo;s Corporate Practice of Medicine doctrine). TechBrot delivers the books inside your established professional entity; entity setup and legal structure are handled by your attorney, and your CPA confirms accounting basis and files.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:15px;">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-07</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-07</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-07 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── RELATED · NY services & industries (r-2 rel-cards). (H2 + 4 H3s) ── #}
